Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:18.59,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Man... Mami-san really is cool, you know!{いやー、やっぱマミさんってカッコイイねえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:21.26,Mami,,0,0,0,,Sheesh... this isn't a show, though.{もう、見世物じゃないのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:26.39,Mami,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to forget to be aware of how dangerous this is.{危ないことしてるって意識は、忘れないでいてほしいわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:27.22,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Yes!{いえーす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:31.85,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It didn't drop a Grief Seed, did it?{グリーフシード、落とさなかったね}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:36.02,QB,,0,0,0,,Because that was a familiar that split off from a witch.{今のは魔女から分裂した使い魔でしかないからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:38.11,QB,,0,0,0,,They don't carry Grief Seeds.{グリーフシードは持ってないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:39.69,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a witch, then...{魔女じゃなかったんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:43.07,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Somehow... we keep failing at this part, don't we?{何か、ここんとこずっとハズレだよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.07,Mami,,0,0,0,,Even a familiar can't be left alone, though.{使い魔だって放っておけないのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:49.08,Mami,,0,0,0,,Since when they mature, they'll grow into a witch like the one from which they originally separated.{成長すれば、分裂元と同じ魔女になるから}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.08,Mami,,0,0,0,,Come, let's go.{さぁ、行きましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.67,Mami,,0,0,0,,Did you two find anything to wish for?{二人とも何か願いごとは見つかった？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:58.25,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You, Madoka?{まどかは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:01.92,Mami,,0,0,0,,Well, it's that kind of thing, you know.{まあ、そういうものよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:03.89,Mami,,0,0,0,,Especially if you're told to think of something immediately.{いざ考えろって言われたら}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:07.01,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Mami-san, what kind of wish did you ask for?{マミさんはどんな願いごとをしたんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:11.43,Madoka,,0,0,0,,No, um... I don't have to hear it no matter what...{いや、あの、どうしても聞きたいってわけじゃなくて}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.98,Mami,,0,0,0,,In my case...{私の場合は}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:29.49,Mami,,0,0,0,,{\t(2573,3408,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&)}I simply did not have room to consider it.{考えている余裕さえなかったってだけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:33.38,Mami,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean I regret it.{後悔しているわけじゃないのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:38.46,Mami,,0,0,0,,I think my current way of life... is greatly preferable to dying in that place.{今の生き方も、あそこで死んじゃうよりは、よほど良かったと思ってる}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:44.72,Mami,,0,0,0,,But you know, I want girls with room for a proper choice to think about precisely what they want.{でもね、ちゃんと選択の余地のある子には、キチンと考えたうえで決めてほしいの}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:48.97,Mami,,0,0,0,,Because that's something I couldn't do... right?{私にできなかったことだからこそ、ね}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.79,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mami-san...{ねえ、マミさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:55.34,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,If your wish isn't for your own benefit, is it forbidden?{願い事って自分の為の事柄でなきゃダメなのかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:55.73,Mami,,0,0,0,,Eh?{え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:59.27,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,For example... this is just an example scenario, okay?{例えば、例えばの話なんだけどさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:03.24,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,If there's a person who's troubled to a greater extent than someone like myself,{私なんかより余程困っている人が居て}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.38,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,and my wish was used for that person's benefit...{その人の為に願い事をするのは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.37,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Is this about Kamijou-kun?{それって上条君のこと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:10.28,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,D–Didn't I say it was just an example scenario!?{例え話だって言ってるじゃんか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:16.08,QB,,0,0,0,,It isn't particularly necessary for the person who's contracting to be the target of the wish, you know.{別に契約者自身が願い事の対象になる必然性はないんだけどね.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.88,QB,,0,0,0,,It isn't an unprecedented situation, either.{前例も無い訳じゃないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.92,Mami,,0,0,0,,But what you're saying isn't too admirable.{でもあまり関心できた話じゃないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:27.39,Mami,,0,0,0,,If you're granting another person's wish, then that's all the more reason to think clearly about your own desires.{他人の願いを叶えるのなら、なおのこと自分の望みをはっきりさせておかないと}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:31.14,Mami,,0,0,0,,Miki-san... do you want his dream to be fulfilled?{美樹さん、あなたは彼に夢を叶えてほしいの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:34.89,Mami,,0,0,0,,Or do you want to be the one who fulfills his dream?{それとも、彼の夢を叶えた恩人になりたいの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.34,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Mami-san...{マミさん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:38.40,Mami,,0,0,0,,They seem the same, but are completely different.{同じようでも全然違うことよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.40,Mami,,0,0,0,,These things.{これ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:43.15,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I think saying it like that was a bit cruel.{その言い方は…ちょっと酷いと思う}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:46.82,Mami,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I had to say it now while I had the chance.{ごめんね。でも今のうちに言っておかないと}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:52.16,Mami,,0,0,0,,Since if you move forward while mistaken about that, you will surely regret it.{そこを履き違えたまま先に進んだら、あなたきっと後悔するから}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:58.37,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That's right.{…そうだね}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:01.04,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,My thoughts were naïve.{私の考えが甘かった}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:02.17,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Sorry.{ゴメン}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:06.09,Mami,,0,0,0,,In the end... this really is a difficult thing, isn't it?{やっぱり、難しい事柄よね}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:08.89,Mami,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't decide in a hurry.{焦って決めるべきではないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:12.85,QB,,0,0,0,,For me, the sooner the better, though.{僕としては、早ければ早い程いいんだけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.22,Mami,,0,0,0,,That's no good.{ダメよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:16.89,Mami,,0,0,0,,Girls hate guys who rush them.{女の子を急かす男子は嫌われるぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:25.57,Madoka,,0,0,0,,In the end, this really isn't something simple, is it?{やっぱり簡単なことじゃないんだよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:28.28,QB,,0,0,0,,I am not allowed to rush you from my position.{僕の立場で急かすわけにはいかないしね}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.62,QB,,0,0,0,,Giving advice is also a violation of the rules.{助言するのもルール違反だし}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:34.74,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's not good to simply want to become one...{ただなりたいってだけじゃダメなのかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:38.54,QB,,0,0,0,,Madoka, do you long for the power itself?{まどかは、力そのものに憧れているのかい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.83,Madoka,,0,0,0,,No, that isn't it...{いや、そんなんじゃなくって}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.88,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it is, though...{そうなのかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:48.51,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I am slow, and I have no redeeming qualities.{私って鈍くさいし、何の取り柄もないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:52.72,Madoka,,0,0,0,,So if I could become someone like Mami-san, who's cool and wonderful...{だからマミさんみたいにカッコよくて素敵な人になれたら}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:55.51,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That alone would bring me enough happiness, or something.{それだけで十分に幸せなんだけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:59.56,QB,,0,0,0,,Madoka, if you became a magical girl, you'd be far stronger than Mami.{まどかが魔法少女になれば、マミよりずっと強くなれるよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:05.32,QB,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's also based on what kind of wish you make when contracting, but...{もちろん、どんな願い事で契約するかにもよるけれど}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:10.07,QB,,0,0,0,,Madoka, measuring the size of the Soul Gem you might produce is impossible, even for me.{まどかが産み出すかもしれないソウルジェムの大きさは、僕にも測定しきれない}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:13.45,QB,,0,0,0,,This is my first time meeting a girl that holds such a natural gift.{これだけの資質を持つ子と出会ったのは初めてだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:18.33,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, what're you saying? That's a lie, right?{何言ってるのよもう…嘘でしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:19.12,QB,,0,0,0,,No—{いや}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.17,Tomohisa,,0,0,0,,Madoka, are you awake?{まどか、起きてるか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:24.09,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what's wrong?{うん、どうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.09,Junko,,0,0,0,,I'm ho—{ただ～い}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:30.59,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Again?{またか}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:31.72,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Really, already...{まったくもう}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.22,Junko,,0,0,0,,W–Water...{み…水…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.64,Junko,,0,0,0,,That bamboo screen baldy...{あのすだれハゲ～}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:45.40,Junko,,0,0,0,,If you want to drink, then pour one for yourself!{飲みたきゃ手酌でやってろっつ～の}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.88,Junko,,0,0,0,,I'll tear it off, with a comb!{めっくらすはらくちゅあ～つ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:47.61,Tomohisa,,0,0,0,,Thank you.{ありがとう}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.99,Tomohisa,,0,0,0,,Should I make hot cocoa?{ココアでも淹れようか}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.53,Junko,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord1.8}It'll be completely clean.{何かすっきり}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.19,Junko,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord1.8}You listening?{聞いてる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.65,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, please.{うん、おねがい}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:55.83,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Why does Mama like her job so much, I wonder?{何でママはあんなに仕事が好きなのかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:08:01.41,Madoka,,0,0,0,,A dream from long ago to work at that company, or something... didn't exist, did it?{昔からあの会社で働くのが夢だった…なんてないよね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:06.84,Tomohisa,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Mama doesn't like her job, she likes persevering.{う～ん…。ママは、仕事が好きなんじゃなくて、がんばるのが好きなのさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:07.34,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Eh?{え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:11.30,Tomohisa,,0,0,0,,I think there are a lot of displeasing and tough things, but...{嫌なことも辛いこともいっぱいあるだろうけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:16.60,Tomohisa,,0,0,0,,The feeling of satisfaction you get after overcoming those things is the greatest treasure for Mama.{それを乗り越えた時の満足感が、ママにとっては最高の宝物なのさ}{for me the greatest feeling of satisfaction is eating a Manzoku Bar}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:23.31,Tomohisa,,0,0,0,,So, working at a company wasn't her dream, you know.{そりゃあ、会社勤めが夢だったわけじゃないだろうけどさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:27.11,Tomohisa,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, Mama is trying to live in her own ideal way.{それでもママは自分の理想の生き方を通してる}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:29.61,Tomohisa,,0,0,0,,Dreams can be fulfilled in that way too.{そんな風にして叶える夢もあるんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:33.11,Madoka,,0,0,0,,The very way you live can become your dream?{生き方そのものを夢にするの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:37.07,Tomohisa,,0,0,0,,I think how you feel about it is up to each individual person, but...{どう思うかは人それぞれだろうけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:40.54,Tomohisa,,0,0,0,,As for me... I love that part about Mama.{僕はね、ママのそういうところが大好きだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:42.37,Tomohisa,,0,0,0,,I can respect it, and take pride in it.{尊敬できるし、自慢できる}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.25,Tomohisa,,0,0,0,,She's a wonderful person, you know.{素晴らしい人だってね}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:46.67,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{うん}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.14,Homura,,0,0,0,,You understand, right?{分かってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:04.52,Homura,,0,0,0,,You have involved ordinary, unrelated people in danger.{貴女は無関係な一般人を危険に巻き込んでいる}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:08.86,Mami,,0,0,0,,The two girls were chosen by Kyubey.{彼女たちはキュゥべえに選ばれたのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.32,Mami,,0,0,0,,They're not unrelated anymore.{もう無関係じゃないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.07,Homura,,0,0,0,,You are guiding both of them to become magical girls.{貴女は二人を魔法少女に誘導している}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:17.20,Mami,,0,0,0,,That's the reason you're not amused?{それが面白くないわけ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.78,Homura,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's bothersome.{ええ、迷惑よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.04,Homura,,0,0,0,,Especially Kaname Madoka.{特に鹿目まどか}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:26.12,Mami,,0,0,0,,I see... You've noticed it as well, then?{そう、あなたも気づいてたのね}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.46,Mami,,0,0,0,,That girl's characteristics.{あの子の素質に}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:31.30,Homura,,0,0,0,,That girl alone... I cannot allow her to form a contract.{彼女だけは、契約させるわけにはいかない}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:34.88,Mami,,0,0,0,,Because an opponent stronger than yourself will be a nuisance?{自分より強い相手は邪魔者ってわけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.68,Mami,,0,0,0,,That's the way a bullied child thinks, you know.{いじめられっ子の発想ね}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:42.35,Homura,,0,0,0,,I don't want to fight with you, though.{貴女とは戦いたくないのだけれど}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:46.77,Mami,,0,0,0,,If that's so, make an extensive effort to see that we never meet again.{なら二度と会うことのないよう努力して}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:51.32,Mami,,0,0,0,,I think tonight will surely be the last time that this will end with just a discussion.{話し合いだけで事が済むのは、きっと今夜で最後だろうから}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.66,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Yo. Sorry for the wait.{よう、お待たせ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:08.71,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Huh? You couldn't meet with Kamijou-kun?{あれ？上条君、会えなかったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:11.50,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Somehow, it looks like today's circumstances were bad, you know.{何か今日は都合悪いみたいでさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:15.09,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Even though I came especially for him... Pretty rude, isn't it?{わざわざ来てやったのに、失礼しちゃうわよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.05,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?{ん？どうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.01,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Over there... there's something...{あそこ…何か…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:26.89,QB,,0,0,0,,It's a Grief Seed!{グリーフシードだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:28.27,QB,,0,0,0,,It's about to hatch!{孵化しかかってる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:31.19,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable! Why in a place like this?{嘘…何でこんなところに}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.27,QB,,0,0,0,,This is bad. We have to escape quickly!{マズいよ、早く逃げないと}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.57,QB,,0,0,0,,A barrier will be completed soon!{もうすぐ結界が出来上がる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.95,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That labyrinth again?{またあの迷路が？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:42.20,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Madoka, have you asked Mami-san for her cell phone number?{まどか、マミさんの携帯、聞いてる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:43.66,Madoka,,0,0,0,,No.{ううん}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:45.41,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,This is bad.{まずったなぁ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.98,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Madoka, go ahead of me and retrieve Mami-san.{まどか、先行ってマミさんを呼んで来て}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.42,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I'll watch over this thing until it's finished.{あたしはこいつを見張ってる}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:51.71,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That's...!{そんな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:52.92,QB,,0,0,0,,Too absurd!{無茶だよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:56.21,QB,,0,0,0,,There is still time before the witch inside emerges,{中の魔女が出てくるまでにはまだ時間があるけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:59.09,QB,,0,0,0,,but when the barrier closes, you won't be able to come outside!{結界が閉じたら、君は外に出られなくなる}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.76,QB,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if Mami's help will make it here in time...{マミの助けが間に合うかどうか}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:05.81,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,When that barrier is completed, you'll end up losing this thing's whereabouts, right?{あの迷路が出来上がったら、こいつの居所も分からなくなっちゃうんでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:11.06,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I can't leave it alone... in a place like this.{放っておけないよ。こんな場所で}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.07,QB,,0,0,0,,Madoka, go on ahead of us and come back.{まどか、先に行ってくれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.32,QB,,0,0,0,,I'll stay close to Sayaka.{さやかには僕が付いてる}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:23.28,QB,,0,0,0,,If Mami comes this far, then she'll understand my position via telepathy.{マミならここまで来れば、テレパシーで僕の位置が分かる}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:28.04,QB,,0,0,0,,If Sayaka and I stay here and watch over the Grief Seed, we'll know the shortest path through the barrier,{ここでさやかと一緒にグリーフシードを見張っていれば、最短距離で結界を抜けられるよう}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.30,QB,,0,0,0,,and then we'll be able to guide Mami.{マミを誘導できるから}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:32.29,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kyubey.{ありがとう、キュウべえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:35.75,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I'll... bring Mami-san back here immediately, then!{私、すぐにマミさんを連れてくるから}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.80,QB,,0,0,0,,Is it scary, Sayaka?{怖いかい？さやか}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:04.03,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That's, well... of course, right?{そりゃあ、まあ、当然でしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:07.18,QB,,0,0,0,,All you need to do is decide on a wish,{願い事さえ決めてくれれば}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:10.87,QB,,0,0,0,,and I can turn you into a magical girl right here and now, though...{今この場で君を魔法少女にしてあげることも出来るんだけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:12.33,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{うん}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:16.00,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,If the time comes, I might have to rely on you.{いざとなったら頼むかも}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.29,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,But right now, I won't.{でも今はやめとく}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.38,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,It's something really important to me, so...{私にとっても、大事な事だから}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:24.89,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,If I do it, I don't want to make a decision with half-hearted feelings.{出来る事なら、いい加減なキモチで決めたくない}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:31.98,Mami,,0,0,0,,Here, right?{ここね}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.90,Mami,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}Kyubey, what's the situation?{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{キュゥべえ、状況は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:42.44,QB,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}We're still all right.{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{まだ大丈夫}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.78,QB,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}There aren't any signs that it will hatch immediately.{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{すぐに孵化する様子はないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.41,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}Sayaka-chan, are you okay?{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{さやかちゃん、大丈夫？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.78,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}I'm fine, I'm fine.{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{平気平気}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.16,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}Bored enough to fall asleep.{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{退屈で居眠りしちゃいそう}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:54.12,QB,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}Actually, it'd be worse if you stimulated the egg by carelessly using large magical powers.{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{むしろ、迂闊に大きな魔力を使って卵を刺激する方がマズい}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:57.49,QB,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}Since you don't need to hurry, could you come as quietly as possible?{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{急がなくていいから、なるべく静かに来てくれるかい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:12:58.17,Mami,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}Understood.{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{わかったわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:13.93,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we made it in time.{間に合ってよかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:16.77,Mami,,0,0,0,,I want to get mad at you for being too rash in doing this, but...{無茶し過ぎ…って怒りたいところだけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:19.94,Mami,,0,0,0,,This time, you made the right decision.{今回に限っては冴えた手だったわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:23.28,Mami,,0,0,0,,With this, any worries about letting the witch get away are—{これなら魔女を取り逃がす心配も}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:27.12,Mami,,0,0,0,,I stated it before, right?{言ったはずよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.62,Mami,,0,0,0,,That I don't want to see you again.{二度と会いたくないって}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:31.33,Homura,,0,0,0,,I'll cut down the game this time.{今回の獲物は私が狩る}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:32.87,Homura,,0,0,0,,You two need to withdraw.{貴女達は手を引いて}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.00,Mami,,0,0,0,,That just won't do.{そうもいかないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.54,Mami,,0,0,0,,We must go meet with Miki-san and Kyubey.{美樹さんとキュゥべえを迎えに行かないと}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.88,Homura,,0,0,0,,I guarantee the safety of those two.{その二人の安全は保証するわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.55,Mami,,0,0,0,,You think I'd trust you?{信用すると思って？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.89,Homura,,0,0,0,,I–Idiot...{ば、馬鹿}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.31,Homura,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to be doing such a thing...{こんなことやってる場合じゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:54.48,Mami,,0,0,0,,Of course, I do not intend to injure you, but...{もちろん怪我させるつもりはないけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:56.64,Mami,,0,0,0,,If you struggle too much, no guarantees.{あんまり暴れたら保障しかねるわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:14:00.77,Homura,,0,0,0,,The witch this time presents a different situation than those guys so far...{今度の魔女は、これまでの奴らとはわけが違う}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:04.15,Mami,,0,0,0,,If you behave, I'll give you a proper release on the way back.{おとなしくしていれば帰りにちゃんと解放してあげる}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.70,Mami,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kaname-san.{行きましょう、鹿目さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:08.32,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Okay.{はい}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:09.95,Homura,,0,0,0,,Wai—{待っ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:40.40,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Um... Mami-san?{あの…マミさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:41.75,Mami,,0,0,0,,What is it?{なあに？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:46.32,Madoka,,0,0,0,,For a wish, I've been thinking about various things in my own way, but...{願いごと、私なりにいろいろと考えてみたんですけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:47.52,Mami,,0,0,0,,Have you decided?{決まりそうなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:50.40,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Yes. But, um...{はい。でも、あの}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:55.37,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you'll get mad at me for thinking about it too lightly, Mami-san.{もしかしたら、マミさんには考え方が甘いって怒られそうで}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.58,Mami,,0,0,0,,What kind of dream do you intend to have fulfilled?{どんな夢を叶えるつもり？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:03.67,Madoka,,0,0,0,,For me... ever since long ago, I've never taken pride in anything like an academic subject, or had a special talent I could boast about.{私って、昔から得意な学科とか、人に自慢できる才能とか何もなくて}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:11.47,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Before this, I always thought that I'd surely go on forever without helping anyone else, merely being a bother.{きっとこれから先ずっと、誰の役にも立てないまま、迷惑ばかりかけていくのかなって}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.39,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I disliked that, yet I couldn't help it.{それが嫌でしょうがなかったんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:25.40,Madoka,,0,0,0,,But I met you, Mami-san, and you showed me what it means to fight for the sake of helping other people.{でもマミさんと会って、誰かを助けるために戦ってるの、見せてもらって}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:30.15,Madoka,,0,0,0,,When I was told that even I could do the same thing...{同じことが、私にもできるかもしれないって言われて}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:34.03,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That made me happier than anything else.{何よりも嬉しかったのはそのことで}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:41.37,Madoka,,0,0,0,,So for me... if I become a magical girl, that will fulfill my wish!{だから私、魔法少女になれたらそれで願いごとは叶っちゃうんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:46.42,Madoka,,0,0,0,,When even someone like me can help other people,{こんな自分でも、誰かの役に立てるんだって}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:48.46,Madoka,,0,0,0,,if I can live with my chest held high...{胸を張って生きていけたら}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.42,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Then that's my number one dream.{それが一番の夢だから}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.34,Mami,,0,0,0,,It's difficult, you know.{大変だよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:55.22,Mami,,0,0,0,,You get injured.{怪我もするし}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:57.93,Mami,,0,0,0,,You won't have free time to fall in love or play around.{恋したり遊んだりしてる暇もなくなっちゃうよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:01.55,Madoka,,0,0,0,,But, Mami-san, who perseveres in spite of that...{でも、それでもがんばってるマミさんに}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:03.27,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I aspire to be like you!{私、憧れてるんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:08.57,Mami,,0,0,0,,I'm not someone you should aspire to be...{憧れるほどのものじゃないわよ、私……}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.15,Mami,,0,0,0,,I'm only forcing myself to put on an appearance...{無理してカッコつけてるだけで}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:15.87,Mami,,0,0,0,,Even though I'm scared and I can barely handle it, I can't go to anyone for consultation.{怖くても辛くても、誰にも相談できないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.66,Mami,,0,0,0,,I can do nothing but cry alone.{一人ぼっちで泣いてばかり}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:21.58,Mami,,0,0,0,,It isn't a pleasant thing... to be something like a magical girl.{いい物じゃないわよ。魔法少女なんて}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.79,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Mami-san, you're not alone or anything anymore.{マミさんはもう一人ぼっちなんかじゃないです}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:31.42,Mami,,0,0,0,,That's right... that's right, isn't it?{そうね。そうなんだよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:40.14,Mami,,0,0,0,,Will you really fight together with me from now on?{本当に、これから私と一緒に戦ってくれるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:43.44,Mami,,0,0,0,,Will you stay by my side?{傍にいてくれるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:46.23,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Yes, if someone like me is okay.{はい、私なんかでよかったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.40,Mami,,0,0,0,,You beat me, didn't you?{参ったなぁ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:52.36,Mami,,0,0,0,,I still have a way to go before I can behave like a proper {\i1}senpai{\i0}, huh...{まだまだちゃんと先輩ぶってなきゃいけないのになぁ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.20,Mami,,0,0,0,,In the end, I'm a useless girl after all.{やっぱり私ダメな子だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.70,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Mami-san...{マミさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:02.37,Mami,,0,0,0,,But you know... since it's a lot of trouble, you should think of something for your wish.{でもさ。せっかくなんだし、願いごとは何か考えておきなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:05.21,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Trouble... is it? As I thought.{せっかく…ですかねぇ、やっぱり}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:09.59,Mami,,0,0,0,,A contract is a contract after all, so think of it as an opportunity to get something.{契約は契約なんだから、ものはついでと思っておこうよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.97,Mami,,0,0,0,,Like billionaire status, or a wonderful boyfriend.{億万長者とか、素敵な彼氏とか}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:14.05,Mami,,0,0,0,,Anything would be fine, wouldn't it? {何だっていいじゃない}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:16.22,Madoka,,0,0,0,,No, that's...{いやぁ…その…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.64,Mami,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll tell you what.{じゃあ、こうしましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:22.31,Mami,,0,0,0,,If you still haven't decided on a wish after this witch is beaten,{この魔女をやっつけるまでに願いごとが決まらなかったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:25.81,Mami,,0,0,0,,then at that time, we'll ask Kyubey to treat us to a cake.{その時は、キュゥべえにご馳走とケーキを頼みましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:27.23,Madoka,,0,0,0,,C–Cake?{ケ、ケーキ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:31.61,Mami,,0,0,0,,That's right. An extravagant celebration cake of the largest size!{そう。最高におっきくて贅沢なお祝いのケーキ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:35.11,Mami,,0,0,0,,And then, we'll have a party with everyone.{それで、みんなでパーティするの}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:38.78,Mami,,0,0,0,,In commemoration of Kaname-san and me becoming a magical girl combo!{私と鹿目さんの、魔法少女コンビ結成記念よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.12,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I'll get a cake for being a magical girl?{私、ケーキで魔法少女に？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.45,Mami,,0,0,0,,If you don't like it, then properly think of something yourself!{嫌ならちゃんと自分で考える}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:46.62,QB,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}Mami!{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{マミ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.79,QB,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}The Grief Seed has started to move...{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{グリーフシードが動き始めた}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.63,QB,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}It's started to hatch. Hurry!{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{孵化が始まる。急いで}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.56,Mami,,0,0,0,,Okay, understood.{オッケー、わかったわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.56,0:17:57.97,Mami,,0,0,0,,I'll finish it this very day with a swift attack!{今日という今日は速攻で片付けるわよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:17:59.64,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That's...!{そんな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:34.50,Mami,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My body feels light.{\i0}{体が軽い}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:38.55,Mami,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the first time I've fought with such a happy feeling...{\i0}{こんな幸せな気持ちで戦うなんて初めて}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.26,Mami,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing is scary anymore!{\i0}{もう何も恐くない━━━！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:51.02,Mami,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm... not someone who's alone!{\i0}{私、一人ぼっちじゃないもの}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:00.57,Mami,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.{お待たせ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.45,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Ah, you made it in time...{間に合ったぁ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:04.72,QB,,0,0,0,,Be careful!{気をつけて}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:05.45,QB,,0,0,0,,It's coming!{出て来るよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.84,Mami,,0,0,0,,Sorry for attacking you at a troublesome time, but I'm going to decide this at once!{せっかくのとこ悪いけど、一気に決めさせて}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:23.68,Mami,,0,0,0,,Take this!{もらうわよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:33.69,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Hurray!{やったぁ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:41.07,Mami,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\bord6\i1\fnMona}★ {\fnImprint MT Shadow\fs130}Tiro{\fnMona}・{\fnImprint MT Shadow\fs130}Finale!!{\fnMona\fs120} ★{\fn\fs}{ティロ・フィナーレ！！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:02.72,Homura,,0,0,0,,It can't be...{まさか}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:12.10,QB,,0,0,0,,You two, contract with me immediately!{二人とも！今すぐ僕と契約を！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.35,QB,,0,0,0,,Madoka! Sayaka!{まどか！さやか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:19.63,QB,,0,0,0,,Decide on your wishes!{願い事を決めるんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:20.19,QB,,0,0,0,,Hurry!{早く}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:21.86,Homura,,0,0,0,,That will not be necessary.{その必要はないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.49,Homura,,0,0,0,,The one who'll kill this thing... is me!{こいつを仕留めるのは、私}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.84,Homura,,0,0,0,,That was a narrow escape from death, you two.{命拾いしたわね、貴女達}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:32.02,Homura,,0,0,0,,Burn that into your eyes.{目に焼き付けておきなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:34.89,Homura,,0,0,0,,That is what it means to become a magical girl.{魔法少女になるって、そういうことよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.00,0:21:52.74,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Return that.{返してよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:56.25,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Return it!{返せよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:22:00.25,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That... that...{それは…それは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:01.42,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,belongs to Mami-san!{マミさんのものだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:04.59,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Didn't I say to return it!? To Mami-san!{返せって言ってるだろ！マミさんに！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:08.86,Homura,,0,0,0,,That's right. This is an item for the benefit of magical girls.{そうよ。これは魔法少女のためのもの}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.86,0:22:11.60,Homura,,0,0,0,,You two don't have the qualifications to touch it.{貴女達には、触る資格なんてない}
