Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.62,0:24:06.29,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,In order to teach us a lesson about what kind of mental preparation is necessary to fight for an objective...{戦う為に、どういう覚悟がいるのか、私達に思い知らせる為に}
